{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":592075,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":122980,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"复旦姚慕生。有配套习题书","timestamp":1605919233,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":592079,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122980,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 谢谢Alice！","timestamp":1605919371,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":592455,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":122980,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"蹲","timestamp":1605927156,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":592551,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":122980,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Linear Algebra Done Right（有中文版）：体系逻辑清晰，motivation明确，读起来不会不明所以。\n姚慕生 高等代数学：几乎没有motivation引入，直接摆定理证明，作为参考感觉还行，cz第一次学的时候用的这个，迷迷糊糊。\n姚慕生 高等代数（上书的配套习题集）：不错，有刷题需求可以考虑，但是当然不能当教材用。\n居余马 大学数学：代数与几何：cz只是比较喜欢这本书的顺序：线性空间-\u003e线性映射-\u003e矩阵作为线性映射在一组基底下的表示-\u003e内积空间，这才是学数学嘛。\n其他的没感觉有很可以的，当然cz看的也不多，最近很多老师用的那个蓝色的自编讲义（梁鑫），cz没看过不知道如何。","timestamp":1605928500,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":592662,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122980,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 哇谢谢Carol！！","timestamp":1605929813,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":122980,"reply":5,"tag":null,"text":"请问dy们线性代数中文教材用的是哪本呀~或者有推荐的中文相关的教材或者辅导书吗？谢谢谢谢！","timestamp":1605919086,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782651,"url":"","vote":{}}}